caption.p: Maximum clade credibility tree for HIV-1 group N using all available env sequences. Sequences from individuals not included in the initial analysis are indicated with a super-script a. The phylogeny was inferred using MrBayes v3.1. Posterior probability values (>0.9) are shown of nodes. Tree is rooted with the SIVcpz sequence that is sister to HIV-1 group N.
